00:43:02,489 --> 00:43:03,650
Ayah.

831
00:43:04,090 --> 00:43:05,359
Ini...

832
00:43:06,659 --> 00:43:08,059
Di sinilah

833
00:43:10,729 --> 00:43:12,559
ibumu berada.

834
00:43:15,669 --> 00:43:16,969
Do Ran.

835
00:43:17,929 --> 00:43:19,940
Setelah melahirkanmu,

